code: @Override protected void readRecords(long lastExpectedRecord) throws Exception {     LOG.debug("readRecords(lastExpectedRecord = {})", lastExpectedRecord).     final LongValue value = new LongValue().     while (running && reader.next(value)) {         final long ts = value.getValue().         if (ts == lastExpectedRecord) {             expectedRecordCounter++.             if (expectedRecordCounter == expectedRepetitionsOfExpectedRecord) {                 break.             }         }     } }
